<br>
Lev does not work.<br>
Due to the intricate keying system, something like 24 players at a time can go.<br>
Because of the process of obtaining keys, these 24 people are going to have to be VERY organized, with a good dps - killing certain creatures spawns a guy who will trade keys for drops, but he does not stick around for long.<br>
Due to that guy I just mentioned, no one should use &quot;/say&quot; for ANYTHING.  He can and will kick your butt for talking in his presence.<br>
A lot of the monsters do not care for duelers, either, though I have heard of that technique being used to complete the Necro epic, at least.<br>
<br>
Last, but not least, go find yourself a list of &quot;what drops what, and what it is used for&quot;.  You should not have time to ask during the raid.<br>
